What is the data structure?

There are many people who hear about Data Structure or what is called Data Structure and do not know what it means.. That is why in this post we will tell you what Data Structure means
So the question we have now - > What does Data Structure mean?
Answer: From its name like this, if we translate it into Arabic, we will find its meaning in structuring data.. I mean, ways to store data and access it quickly when we need it, but that is how simple it is.
